Thereafter, throughout the course of the project, five (5) additional work

7.
Throughout the course of the project, additional work was performed at
the request of the owner totaling $3,025.16. This includes a returned check fee for a
check made out to the lienor as payment for the project which was returned.
8.
In sum, the total agreed upon price for labor performed and materials
furnished was $83,136.16.
9.
The labor was performed and material was furnished beginning on or
about January 23, 2021.
10.
The labor performed and material furnished included but was not limited
to: demolition; framing; supply and installation of cabinets; supply and installation of
countertops; supply and installation of flooring; supply and installation of radiant heat;
supply and installation of electric; supply and installation of plumbing.
11. Throughout the course of the project the owner made payments as
follows on the corresponding dates:
a.
$15,000.00 on January 23, 2021;
b.
$12,000.00 on March 28, 2021;
c.
$15,000.00 on April 30, 2021;
d.
$20,000.00 on June 4, 2021;
